{
  "verses": [
    {
      "verse_num": "1",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "How long, Lord, are you going to forget me? Forever? How long will you turn away from me?\n"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "2",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "How long must I be in inner turmoil, feeling sad all day long? How long will my enemy be victorious over me?"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "3",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Think about this, and answer me, Lord my God. Give me back my strength,  otherwise I'm going to die,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "4",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "and my enemy will say,"
        },
        {
          "type": "speech",
          "text": "I defeated him!",
          "speaker": "Unknown"
        },
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "and my opponents will celebrate my downfall."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "5",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "But I trust in your never-failing love, I will be happy because you save me."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "6",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I will sing to the Lord because he has treated me with such generosity!"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    }
  ]
}